node.title: Firefighters extinguish blaze in Auckland apartment building
node.description: Eight fire trucks attended the fire on Kingston Street this morning, containing it before it could spread to other floors.
node.content:
["Firefighters have put out a blaze on the 20th floor of an inner-city apartment building in Auckland this morning.", "", "
(File image) Photo: RNZ / Nate McKinnon
", "Eight fire trucks attended the fire on Kingston Street, containing it before it could spread to other floors.", "Fire and Emergency said the building was safely evacuated, and no one was injured.", "One lane remains blocked on Hobson Street while emergency services carry out their work."]
